{"tid":1969781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[拜手足定燒手足?]沙嶺公墓現山火　消防撲救1小時後救熄　墓地安葬無名亡者","createTime":"2020-04-12T16:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T17:36:44.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12ccd162d75db2bc2c3d07fee98054c9b63db12b","tid":1969781,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"清明節前後，不時有人到位於羅湖的沙嶺公墓祭亡者，該處墓碑上刻劃的只有編號和日期，沒有姓名與照片，因安葬的是無人認領的亡者。惟今午（12日）2時許，沙嶺公墓突然發生火警，火場面積約10米乘20米，其間多人報警求助。消防員接報到場，約1小時後將火救熄，事件中無人受傷，亦毋須疏散。現場所見，墓碑附近的草地燒至焦黑。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，沙嶺公墓於50年代啟用，是政府為無人認領屍體而設的墳場。公墓位處文錦渡附近，羅湖管制站旁邊，亦鄰近新屋嶺拘留中心，市民毋須申領禁區紙，可自由出入公墓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVZDD1_UcAYrnJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEVZDD1_UcAYrnJg.jpg&h=13f51d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVZDDatUUAAV4eU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEVZDDatUUAAV4eU.jpg&h=4fd5d6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVZDEMsU8AEhNTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEVZDEMsU8AEhNTL.jpg&h=1f2d8d1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9a4e6ffbd37c4dcc60543ca644f1451792cf4f2","tid":1969781,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"死黑警連過左身既手足都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf1a9a5ddfaf91f09aee91d7af5fb4e0bbec540","tid":1969781,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9a4e6ffbd37c4dcc60543ca644f1451792cf4f2","tid":1969781,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"死黑警連過左身既手足都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi